{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_09_01",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 1話 今の私は挑戦者",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。すみれはいつも時間ぴったりだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. You’re always right on time‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "実は子役時代に、時間は必ず守れって教えられたんです\nそう教わってから、遅刻はゼロなんですよ。えっへん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I was taught to always be on time when I was a child actor.\nSince then‚ I’ve never been late. Ahem!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "凄いな。俺も今日からすみれを見習うよ\nところで、折り入って相談があるって聞いたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s amazing. I should learn from you‚ Sumire.\nBy the way‚ I heard you wanted to talk to me about something important?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4000013988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。実は……\n今お話しした、子役時代のお仕事に関係してるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Actually…\n…It’s related to my work as a child actor that I just mentioned.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9333347321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "無理だったらいいんです。私のわがままですし\nでも、もし可能性があるなら、私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay if it’s not possible. It’s just a selfish request‚\nbut if there’s a chance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4666695913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "……もう一度、役者のお仕事をやってみたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’d like to try acting again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5333352407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それって今まですみれが自分から断っていた仕事だよな\n今はアイドルで、もう役者じゃないからって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that’s the kind of work you’ve been turning down‚ Sumire.\nYou said you’re an idol now‚ not an actress anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8666695913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "はい。でも実はずっと前から、また演技の仕事を\nやってみたい、って気持ちはあったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. But to be honest‚ for a long time now‚\nI’ve wanted to do some acting work again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.733336258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、一度役者を辞めた私が復帰するなんて\n本気でやっている方々に失礼だと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I thought returning to the industry would be\ndisrespectful to those who are serious about acting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1000029247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それで躊躇してたんだな。でも、どうして今になって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you were hesitating because of that. But why now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4000029247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "この前、私達トリエルは、VENUSプログラム五位の\nグループに挑戦したじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A while ago‚ we‚ TRINITYAiLE‚ challenged the fifth-ranked group\nin the VENUS program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.833336258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "その時……強く感じたんです\n私達が一番輝けるのは、力を全部出し切った時だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At that time… I strongly felt that\nwe shine the brightest when we give it our all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.933336258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "私は、本当は演技の仕事に未練があったくせに\n「自分はもうアイドルだから役者はやらない」――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I still had lingering feelings for acting…\n“I’m an idol now‚ so I don’t act.”――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6666695913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "って言い訳して、演技の仕事から目を背けてきたんです\nそして自分の可能性を、自分で狭めてきたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I kept making excuses and turning away from acting.\nAnd I limited my own potential.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8666695913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "だから、もう一度演技の仕事に本気で向き合いたい\nその挑戦が私を、そしてトリエルを成長させてくれる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I want to face acting seriously once again.\nI believe that challenge will help me grow‚ and TRINITYAiLE too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3666695913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "そういう風に思って……\n……ダメでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what I think…\n…Is it impossible?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.433336258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "すみれの気持ちは分かった\nでもすみれは、役者としてブランクがある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you feel‚ Sumire.\nBut you’ve been on hiatus as an actress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.9000029247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりいい作品に出演出来る訳じゃない\nオーディションを受けることになるけど……いいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can’t just land a role in a good production right away.\nYou’ll have to audition… is that alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.6000029247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです。今の私は挑戦者なんですから\nそれが当たり前だと思います。だからやらせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. I’m a challenger now.\nThat’s only natural. So please let me do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.0000029247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "元子役の私じゃなくて、今の私がどれだけやれるのか\n見ていて下さいね、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Watch what I can do now‚ not as the child actor I used to be‚\nbut as who I am today‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.433336258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、応援とサポートは任せてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ leave the cheering and support to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.3666996003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　{user}さんが\n応援してくれるなら無敵です！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay~! If {user}-san\nsupports me‚ then I’m invincible!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.833336258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今、星見プロに来ているオーディションの案内は……\nこの映画だな。興味はあるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ the audition notices we have at Hoshimi Pro are…\nfor this movie. Are you interested?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.5666675568,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2833.3663940999827,
          "startTime": 186.4000339509
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "見せて下さい！　どれどれ……これは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me see! Hmm hmm… this is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.4000339509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living_evening",
      "startTime": 194.0167077384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "ご主人様、お茶を淹れました。……どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Master‚ I’ve made you some tea. …Please enjoy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.0667077384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとう。そこに置いておいてくれ\n……いや、くれたまえ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ thank you. You can leave it there.\n…No‚ please give it to me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.833336258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "どうして語尾が疑問形なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you ending your sentences with question marks?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.7667077384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "慣れてないからだよ……。なぁ、すみれ\n他の人にかわってもらう方がいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s because I’m not used to it… Hey‚ Sumire.\nWouldn’t it be better to have someone else do this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.2666666667,
